<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.10.2">
<l>veṉṟimiku narakaṉura matuvaḻiya viciṟum viṟalāḻit taṭakkaiyaṉ viṇṇavarkaṭ kaṉṟu</l>
<l>kuṉṟukoṭu kuraikaṭalaik kaṭaintamuta maḷikkum kurumaṇiyeṉ ṉāramutaṅ kulaviyuṟai kōyil</l>
<l>eṉṟumiku peruñcelvat teḻilviḷaṅku maṟaiyō rēḻicaiyuṅ kēḷvikaḷu miyaṉṟaperuṅ kuṇattōr</l>
<l>aṉṟulakam paṭaittavaṉai yaṉaiyavarkaḷ nāṅkū rarimēya viṇṇakaram vaṇaṅkumaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Simple heart, worship in Arimēya Viṇṇakaram in Nānkūr</l>
<l rend="indent">with those who are like the one who created the world long ago,</l>
<l rend="indent">those of great qualities suited to scholarship and the seven melodies,</l>
<l>[And] experts in the Vedas, whose beauty of superior</l>
<l rend="indent">great learning always shines,</l>
<l>The temple where dwells my precious nectar, rejoicing,</l>
<l rend="indent">the dark jewel who bestowed nectar that day to the celestials,</l>
<l rend="indent">churning the roaring sea with a mountain,</l>
<l>He in whose wide hand is the victorious discus,</l>
<l rend="indent">which he hurled so that the power of Naraka,</l>
<l rend="indent">whose victories were increasing, was destroyed.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
